                    (6) proof of address.
                  </p> <p>We look forward to welcome you aboard.</p> <br><br> <p>Sincerely, </p><br> <p>For <b></b><br>HR DEPARTMENT <br> Date: <br>Location: </p></div></div></div></div></div> <div class="modal-footer text-center"><button type="button" data-dismiss="modal" class="btn btn-danger">
